Interface LanguageResourceResolver

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.sonar.api.BatchComponent, org.sonar.api.BatchExtension, org.sonar.api.Extension
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    JavaResourceResolver

    public interface LanguageResourceResolver
extends org.sonar.api.BatchExtension
    Defines an interface for resolving resources representing language specific elements, e.g. java classes.
